                <head>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">notice of ratification by mexico</hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Translation.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Embassy of Mexico to the United States of
                                America</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1905-05-22">
                            <hi rend="italic">May 22, 1905</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                    <seg rendition="#left">No. 174.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Honorable Sir</hi>: I have the honor to inform you, for all
                    pertinent purposes, that on the 1st day of the current month, as the department
                    of foreign relations of Mexico has been pleased to advise me, the Government of
                    the Republic ratified the treaty relative to claims for pecuniary damages and
                    injuries that was signed in the said city of Mexico on the 30th day of January,
                    1902, by the delegates to the Second International American Conference.</p>
                <p>Accept, honorable sir, the renewed assurances of my very high consideration.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">F. Gamboa</hi>,<lb/>
                        <hi rend="italic">Chargé d’ Affaires ad Interim.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
                <postscript>
                    <p>Hon. <hi rend="smallcaps">Francis B. Loomis</hi>,<lb/>
                        <hi rend="italic">Acting Secretary of State.</hi>
                    </p>
                </postscript>
            </div>
        </body>
